=Bio=

"Dr. Peiyuan Guo is co-founder and General Manager of SynTao. As one of China’s renowned experts in Corporate Social Responsibility (CSR) and Socially Responsible Investment (SRI), he has been closely involved in responsible management development. Dr. Guo holds a rich experience in consulting, research and training services, he is a highly appreciated speaker at international conferences and he is a selection committee member for a number of prestigious CSR awards. Before the foundation of SynTao, Dr. Guo gained work experience at the United Nations, the World Trade Organization and West LB."



